title: Gibson Exhaust shows their Power Curves on 2015 Ford Mustang GT 5.0
description:
Gibson Power Curves model McKenzie Jo Lowetter heats up the studio with all new 2015 Mustang GT 5.0 featuring the Gibson Performance 3" Dual Exhaust System.  

Boasting dyno tested gains of 32 horsepower and 34 ft-lbs of Torque, the 3" exhaust system creates a strong throaty sound that leaves that stock exhaust in tire smoke!

4.5" Intercooled Stainless Tips
3" Equal Length X-Pipe
Dual SuperFlow Mufflers
3" Mandrel Bent Tubing

Stainless System, Part # 619013
Elite Black Ceramic, Part # 619013-B

American-Made exhaust system with a Lifetime Limited Warranty to ensure satisfaction is guaranteed.
